# Marlin-PID-processor

The processor can be used for producing sample to train the TMVA, or use the TMVA weight files for charged particle identification. A ilcsoft package is needed.

1.Install

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -C $ILCSOFT/ILCSoft.cmake ..
make install

cd ..
source env.sh

2.Sample producing 

With your own simulated sample at different energy points, (here is (1,2,3,5,7,10,20,30,40,50,70) by default, you can change it sub_PID)

